data.description: HUGE Price Reduction & Lowest price per sqft!! **MOTIVATED SELLERS** This is a MUST-SEE home with a 1% Sellers Concession of sales price towards rate buydown - VACANT & READY FOR MOVE-IN - Welcome Home to this gorgeous 5 Bedroom/4.5 Bath, Perry built home on large lot (0.27 acres) in one of Austin’s best Master-Planned community. This spacious home highlights a two-story entry with curved staircase followed by an amazing open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining. Featuring library/office with French doors, formal dining, gourmet kitchen with walk-in pantry, butler's pantry and large kitchen island, Two-story family room with wall of windows and corner fireplace opens to island kitchen. Ceramic tile floors throughout main areas. Primary suite includes bedroom with curved wall of windows, Dual vanities, garden tub, separate glass-enclosed shower and two walk-in closets in primary bath. Downstairs guest suite with dedicated full bath and walk-in closet. Upstairs gameroom and adjacent media room, computer area + 3 additional bedrooms and 2 full baths. Abundant storage space throughout. Extended covered backyard patio is leading out to your spacious backyard that is large enough to build the pool of your dreams. 3 car tandem garage. Minutes away to Bryson's “The Backyard“ amenity center, resort-style pool, ‘River Splash Pad’, fire-pit, event lawn, playground, TV-lounge, outdoor pavilion, catch & release pond, and upcoming dog park. Over 3 miles of hike & bike trails along Bryson creek and woods. Zoned for sought-after Leander ISD. Great location with retail shopping and restaurants nearby. Easy access to 183 for your commute to Austin or you can take the Leander Metro Rail which is minutes away from Bryson. This community truly has something for everyone, so don’t miss out on this opportunity to own your home and enjoy watching fireflies in your backyard & counting shooting stars in the Texas sky. Motivated Sellers!
